title: The Strengths and Weaknesses of the Potential Playoff Teams | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Ryan and Cole discuss the strengths and weaknesses of the division leaders and the wild-card teams in the AFC (4:10) and the NFC (31:09). They also talk about a couple more teams in each conference that will be fighting for that final wild-card spot in the second half of the season.
Hosts: Ryan Shazier and Cole Wright
